Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.88,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Follow me Follow you 唯愿相通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.92,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}释放这沸腾热血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:57.35,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}战栗在冲突之中 从天而降的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:02.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}可要过早地将早熟的果实 吞噬殆尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:08.09,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}几度挣扎 总不忘仰问苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:11.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}确认你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:16.03,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}无意与人假装和气 徒增太多恸哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:21.29,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}混乱在纠葛之中 只为活在当下
