Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:35.26,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（营业中&七夕准备中）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多回收了9成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能赶上今天的祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑学长 写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:44.14,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（想活下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了啦 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写最坦率的愿望就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赌在了可能性上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非和平之路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的牺牲者踏上旅途之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛也迎来了希望与危机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍穹之FAFNER EXODUS 第6话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福之时
